TopicTitle: Sector Seven Space Laboratories Airlines Division reveals the SS 327 Transporter

Articles.Content:
During our plans to build a Global Transporter we designed a new passenger compartment allowing the customers to experience the effects of a wind tunnel, we got the name 327 from Three Cockpits and a total of 27 personnel. Planning to release the craft file on the Spacecraft Exchange Forum at a later date.

Wait! are those Kerbals in there?
